    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/7475a31da41f8617b1ecc94e624381ac.poster.avif?t=1752664639\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/7475a31da41f8617b1ecc94e624381ac.webm?t=1752664639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/7475a31da41f8617b1ecc94e624381ac.mp4?t=1752664639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在和平的森林里，植物和动物开始了战争！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为守护森林的妖精，踏上一段拯救被诅咒污染的森林的一日旅程。从明亮的清晨到夕阳西下的黄昏，再到黑暗的夜晚，激烈的战斗一触即发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个序章中，您可以体验唤醒森林清晨的3场战斗以及日落时分的1场战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/77ad0f9cb21ef96a30141fb3716f65a7.poster.avif?t=1752664639\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/77ad0f9cb21ef96a30141fb3716f65a7.webm?t=1752664639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/77ad0f9cb21ef96a30141fb3716f65a7.mp4?t=1752664639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守护基地并击败敌方首领</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要净化被诅咒的森林并召唤友军，您需要一个叫“蘑菇塔”的基地。保护蘑菇塔免受蜂拥而至的敌攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌会在他们的首领被击败之前持续进攻。利用有限的法力召唤动物友军并使用技能来推进前线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/4c0c36ca798bb94457b6fa740712e8aa.poster.avif?t=1752664639\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/4c0c36ca798bb94457b6fa740712e8aa.webm?t=1752664639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315400/extras/4c0c36ca798bb94457b6fa740712e8aa.mp4?t=1752664639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成长卡组</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着从清晨到黄昏，再到夜晚的推进，敌人会越来越强。为取得战斗胜利，我们的友军也需要变得更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得更好的动物卡牌，并为动物配上具有强化效果的帽子。妖精的技能卡和护符也是通往胜利策略的一部分！</p>",
